body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting our customer support. My name is Jason Cox and I work for Superior Cars Inc. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Megan Allen.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Megan. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling frustrated because the security system in my car seems to be malfunctioning.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm sorry to hear that. To assist you further, could you please provide me with the vehicle identification number (VIN) of your car? It's a sequence of seventeen characters.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the VIN number is one two three four five six seven eight nine zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. One more piece of information I need is your current location in latitude and longitude coordinates. Do you have that available?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, my coordinates are thirty seven point four zero five two latitude and one two one point nine eight seven longitude.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Megan. I'll escalate this issue to our technical team for further assistance. I appreciate your cooperation. Is there anything else I can help with?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that will be all. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Megan. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
